<p>When i add an scroll to my textarea then the textarea isnt visible in the application:</p>  <p>Code:</p>  <pre><code>    JPanel panel = new JPanel();     frame.getContentPane().add(panel, BorderLayout.CENTER);     panel.setLayout(null);      final JTextArea textArea = new JTextArea();      textArea.setBounds(15, 112, 689, 310);     JScrollPane scrollPane = new JScrollPane( textArea );      panel.add( scrollPane ); </code></pre>